name: Tree House
description:
Tree House

This is Tree House, a game where you have to build your houses across the whole of the woodland.  Clicking on a tree will convert it to a house, however the surrounding houses and trees will also change, presenting you with a rather puzzling problem.

This is my contribution to the Nothing Stays Forever weekly game jam, number 160.

Good luck!
